data.description: More than 61 acres of sprawling fields and woods with trails perfect for horseback riding or hunting. This charming 2BR/1BA expanded rancher features hardwood floors, exposed brick, and plenty of room for outdoor entertaining. A separate office space is perfect for working from home. The mudroom just off the eat-in country kitchen is ideal for equestrians hoping to make use of the 6-stall barn and newly fenced pastures. This property is just seconds from Janemark Winery and offers so many possibilities with a party barn, small workshop, and the possibility of creating more lots.
